(Palace of Tranquility)

69
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,160
♪I miss you a lot♪

70
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:41,830
♪But I pretend I don't♪

71
00:02:42,360 --> 00:02:46,080
♪We met hurriedly
and you stole my heart♪

72
